OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a largely cloudy day
OL,6,Fbut staying mainly dry with light
OL,7,Fwinds. A little light rain is
OL,8,Fpossible, mainly across the
OL,9,FCairngorms. Some bright spells
OL,10,Fdeveloping in the afternoon along the
OL,11,FMoray Coast.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA cloudy evening for most
OL,14,Fwith a few light showers around. Clear
OL,15,Fspells along the Moray Coast will
OL,16,Fdevelop more widely across most areas
OL,17,Fovernight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
