OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FDry through the morning and
OL,6,Ffor much of the afternoon with good
OL,7,Fsunny spells. Turning cloudy with some
OL,8,Fshowers spreading east through late
OL,9,Fafternoon and evening.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FA
OL,12,Fmixture of sunshine and showers on
OL,13,FTuesday and Wednesday, the showers
OL,14,Fwintry on the hills. Some rain
OL,15,Fpossible on Thursday. Feeling cool for
OL,16,Fthe time of year.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
